# Domain-Context Loader Template

Create one rule per major domain. Copy this template and customize:

```yaml
---
description: "Load <domain> context when editing related files."
globs:
  - <relevant/path/**>
alwaysApply: false
---
```

## Rule body

```markdown
# <Domain> Context

Before changing files under <path>/, read [docs/agent-context/<domain>.md].
Do not duplicate that file inline — follow its conventions in your edits.
```

This pattern keeps rules lightweight (auto-loaded by glob) while domain details live in full docs that agents load on demand.
